Package: EVICC
Title: Modular Time Series Plotting with Plotly and Enhancements
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Gerard", "Grande", email = "ggrande@ari.ad", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides modular tools to construct and enhance time series plots using plotly. 
    Includes support for conditional coloring, moving averages, trend lines, and vertical year markers 
    in a composable pipeline style.
